(7, 1, '2020-08-03 01:23:44', '2020-08-03 01:23:44', '<img width=\"1024\" height=\"427\" src=\"http://localhost/dislyshop/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/jam-3-1024x427.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/dislyshop/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/jam-3-1024x427.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/dislyshop/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/jam-3-300x125.jpg 300w, http://localhost/dislyshop/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/jam-3-768x320.jpg 768w, http://localhost/dislyshop/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/jam-3-1536x640.jpg 1536w, http://localhost/dislyshop/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/jam-3-2048x854.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\">\n\n10/10 First exclusive and&nbsp; the most complete watch store in Balikpapan. Selling almost all famous watch brands with high quality and extraordinary services. I\'m really pleased to buy watch here.\n\n-XPLRM local reviewer\n\n<img width=\"499\" height=\"499\" src=\"http://localhost/dislyshop/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/gshock-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/dislyshop/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/gshock-2.jpg 499w, http://localhost/dislyshop/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/gshock-2-300x300.jpg 300w, http://localhost/dislyshop/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/gshock-2-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 499px) 100vw, 499px\">\n<img width=\"700\" height=\"700\" src=\"http://localhost/dislyshop/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/skmei.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/dislyshop/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/skmei.jpg 700w, http://localhost/dislyshop/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/skmei-300x300.jpg 300w, http://localhost/dislyshop/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/skmei-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\">\n\nThe experience of buying online on the website is surprisingly easy and&nbsp;convenient. Messages were answered with fast responses, product sent immediately after payment, and the quality of watch itself is excellent.\n\n-Jekstun local reviewer', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2020-08-03 11:14:55', 