(14, 1, '2020-08-03 01:30:40', '2020-08-03 01:30:40', '<h2>THE BRAND, THE MISSION, AND THE PEOPLE BEHIND DISLY SHOP.</h2>		\n		<p>Disly Shop was opened in 2002. We started the business in online shop form. We took the photo of the watches and publish it in a website and some social medias. We didn\'t expect anything back then as we sold watches just to get money and survive.</p>\n<p>The idea of selling watches came from our second daughter named Dysdys. She were excited about online shopping and started to think \"Why am i not selling things online as well? Since online selling could get me more money to buy stuffs\". She started looking for some watch factories to get the lowest price possible, so she could sell it with lower price than the market so her online shop can attract the consumer.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The business unexpectedly blows up. There are a lot of customers that were loved her product. Seeing this, our family decided to make an offline store for this business and the shop is here till now.</p>		\n										<img width=\"512\" height=\"383\" src=\"http://localhost/dislyshop/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/toko.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://localhost/dislyshop/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/toko.jpg 512w, http://localhost/dislyshop/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/toko-300x224.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" />											\n		<h1>Our shop in 2002&nbsp;</h1><h1>Balikpapan</h1>', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2020-08-03 10:38:15', '2020-08-03 10:38:15', '', 0, 'http://localhost/dislyshop/?page_id=14', 0, 'page', '', 0),
